name: flashgeotext
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flashgeotext" %}
{% set version = "0.4.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e2cdf8eb26a1e49544f61f081b45e9b20410209028a7c1a1425711921fdbb6ae

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - flashtext >=2.7,<3.0
    - loguru >=0.5.3,<0.7.0
    - pip
    - poetry-core >=1.0.0,<2.0.0
    - pydantic >=1.8,<2.0
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - flashtext >=2.7,<3.0
    - loguru >=0.5.3,<0.7.0
    - pydantic >=1.8,<2.0
    - python >=3.6

test:
  imports:
    - flashgeotext

about:
  home: https://flashgeotext.iwpnd.pw
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Extract and count countries and cities (+their synonyms) from text
  doc_url: https://flashgeotext.iwpnd.pw
  dev_url: https://github.com/iwpnd/flashgeotext

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - iwpnd
    - francbartoli
